## Original Task ID: WEC-39
## Priority: None
## Status: In Progress

Update the color scheme to be more vibrant as the client says the current colors are too faint. Implement a warmer color palette with higher contrast and orange accent color.

## Subtasks
- [ ] WEC-39-1: Update CSS root variables with new color values
- [ ] WEC-39-2: Update UI elements to use new color scheme
- [ ] WEC-39-3: Update calendar styling with new colors
## Files
- `includes/css/ydcoza-styles.css`
## Comments
- {
  "text": "Questions for Client Clarification:

1. Top Bar & Sidebar:
- When specifying 'No background', should it be transparent or white?
- Should this apply to both mobile and desktop views?

2. Alert Background:
- Should #44546f apply to all alert types or specific ones?
- What should the text color be for these alerts?

3. Form Labels:
- When specifying 'background: none', are we removing an existing background?
- What size/color should the bold text be?

4. Button States:
- What color should the hover outline be?
- Should text color change on hover?
- What should the border-radius be?

5. Main Button:
- What should be the text color?
- What color should the hover outline effect be?
- Is this style only for section-bottom placement?

6. Icons:
- Is #94c748 only for dark background icons?
- What color for light background icons?
- Does this apply to all icons or specific sets?

Proposed CSS Implementation:

```css
:root {
    --accent: #1d7afc;
    --main-action: #216e4e;
    --icon-dark-bg: #94c748;
    --form-border: #b3b9c4;
    --alert-bg: #44546f;
}

body {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
}

.ydcoza-compact-form input[type=email],
.ydcoza-compact-form input[type=number],
.ydcoza-compact-form input[type=password],
.ydcoza-compact-form input[type=search],
.ydcoza-compact-form input[type=tel],
.ydcoza-compact-form input[type=text],
.ydcoza-compact-form input[type=url],
.ydcoza-compact-form select,
.ydcoza-compact-form textarea {
    border: 1px solid var(--form-border);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 5px 10px;
}

.ydcoza-compact-form .form-label {
    background: none;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.btn-primary {
    background-color: var(--accent);
    padding: 0.5em 1.5em;
}

.btn-main-action {
    background-color: var(--main-action);
    padding: 0.5em 1.5em;
}

h5 {
    margin-top: 2em;
}

.dark-bg .icon {
    color: var(--icon-dark-bg);
}
```"
}

